            </div>
            
            <div class="grid-2">
                <div class="testimonial-card">
                    <p style="color: #ffa500; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 15px;">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ 5/5</p>
                    <p style="font-style: italic; color: #607d8b; line-height: 1.8;">"An absolutely magical experience! The team organized everything perfectly. The tea plantation tour was unforgettable!"</p>
                    <p style="font-weight: 600; color: #263238; margin-top: 15px;">- Sarah Mitchell, USA</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="testimonial-card">
                    <p style="color: #ffa500; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 15px;">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ 5/5</p>
                    <p style="font-style: italic; color: #607d8b; line-height: 1.8;">"Best vacation ever! The safari in Yala was incredible. Can't wait to go back!"</p>
                    <p style="font-weight: 600; color: #263238; margin-top: 15px;">- James Chen, Singapore</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="testimonial-card">
                    <p style="color: #ffa500; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 15px;">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ 5/5</p>
                    <p style="font-style: italic; color: #607d8b; line-height: 1.8;">"Incredible guides, amazing food, breathtaking views. TravelApp made our dream Sri Lankan vacation real!"</p>
